node.text: Wanted to remind you to never take a day for granted. That you are so worthy of this life and strong enough to live it. Our physical bodies may have expiration dates but our souls do not!! 🤍💭 live your life! Do what makes you happy! Sorry for the tears but when I feel these things I know in my heart it’s because I’m meant to share them... I love you. Keep going. Keep fighting. Keep the faith.

node.text: Proud LA girl! Sang the National Anthem at the 🖤💗 @intermiamicf VS 💙💛 @lagalaxy game. Thanks for the invitation @davidbeckham & @davegrutman!

node.title: Inter Miami CF vs. LA Galaxy | National Anthem

node.text: So much love to all of the beautiful guests who came to our @treslucebeauty Miami event. 🥰 It meant so much to me to have you all there. Thank you to everyone who made it all possible! One more thing… INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING will be available to 150 countries this Wednesday 7/28!!!! 🤗 I know you’ve been patiently waiting 🙌🏽 Soooo excited for everyone to have #TresluceBeauty in their hands worldwide!! 💙💙💙
